## RULE 10 — Channel Number: Always Cast to int (LL-010)

FastAPI path parameters arrive as `str`. Database `Channel.number` is `int`. Always
cast before comparison. Never rely on SQLite coercion.

```python
# WRONG
stmt = select(Channel).where(Channel.number == channel_number)  # str vs int

# CORRECT
stmt = select(Channel).where(Channel.number == int(channel_number))
```

Wrap in try/except and raise `HTTPException(400)` on `ValueError`.

