## RULE 13 — Muxrate: Always Explicit int Cast (LL-016)

Muxrate calculations combining profile fields MUST use explicit `int()` casts.
Profile fields may be stored as strings in the database.

```python
# WRONG
f"{profile.video_bitrate + profile.audio_bitrate}k"  # silent str concat

# CORRECT
f"{int(profile.video_bitrate) + int(profile.audio_bitrate)}k"
```

